result.name: list-of-educational-psychology-trainees
result.notes: Educational psychology training is a three year doctorate programme. NCTL train on average 120 annually and share the cost with employers.  There are contractual implications for both trainees receiving government funding for the course and training providers, particularly for those trainees deferring or leaving the course. This dataset is a list of trainees who are in training or have deferred or left the course or have completed training since 2009.
